name: Dark Magician of Black Chaos
effect:
You can Ritual Summon this card with "Chaos Form".
This card is treated as "Magician of Black Chaos" while on the field, and as "Dark Magician" while in the GY.
If this card is Ritual Summoned: You can add 1 "Chaos Scepter" card from your Deck or GY to your hand.
While you control this card, you can activate Quick-Play Spell Cards from your hand during your opponent's turn.
